Dataset brief description: This dataset shows where you can buy a reusable cup, get a discount for using it and other nearby places to recycle single-use cups. It represents a map built on a community driven challenge. In addition it is downloadable in multiple linked data formats including RDF AND JSON-LD.

Dataset name: Bibliotecas de Roma. Lista completa de registros bibliográficos en el Catálogo de las Bibliotecas de Roma en 2020
Dataset brief description: This dataset contains a  complete list of bibliographic records in the Catalogue of the Libraries of Rome in 2020
The RDF book mashup makes information about books, their authors, reviews, and online bookstores available on the Semantic Web.
